# Shopify rules (future /api/shop/*)

## Contract first

- Treat `/api/shop/*` as your stable internal API surface for the frontend.
- Never expose Shopify access tokens to the browser.

## Token safety

- Shopify credentials live in Worker env vars.
- Use `.dev.vars` locally and `wrangler secret put` in production.

## Error handling

- Always return a JSON body with `error.code` and `error.message` fields for `/api/shop/*`.
